snippet.title: Pioneer - Drone Flight
snippet.description:
Hi there!

I've finally had some time to work on my game again and i have made good progress. After some consideration, the Beta will be released sometime in February 2025!

If you'd like to join the Beta feel free to contact me anywhere. ❤️
